Package: POMA
Title: R Package for Statistical Analysis of Mass Spectrometry Data
Version: 1.5.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Pol",
           family = "Castellano-Escuder",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "polcaes@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6466-877X"))
Description: POMA is an easy use R package that contains different robust functions for processing, exploratory analysis and statistical analysis of mass spectrometry data, such as metabolomics or proteomics. This package is based on the standardized "MSnbase" infrastructure to achieve maximum flexibility and reproducibility. This package also offers a Shiny app that implements all functions in an easy use web interface.
